@section Files@comma{} Diffs@comma{} and Operations

Start here after choosing a revision in the log.  These inspection workflows
share the repository and revision context of the buffer that opened them@comma{} but
some editing and recovery actions are explicitly identified below.

@menu
* Diffing::
* File and Blob Inspection::
