@findex majutsu-annotate-addition
Enter annotate from a blob buffer. From an ordinary file buffer@comma{} use @samp{M-x majutsu-annotate-addition}. When invoked again on an annotated chunk@comma{} jump to its parent revision (when available) and re-annotate there.
@item @kbd{c} (@code{majutsu-annotate-cycle-style})
