Move to the next or previous chunk.
@item @kbd{C-j / g j / C-k / g k (Evil)} (@code{majutsu-annotate-next-chunk / majutsu-annotate-previous-chunk})
@kindex C-j / g j / C-k / g k (Evil)
@findex majutsu-annotate-next-chunk / majutsu-annotate-previous-chunk
Move to the next or previous chunk.
