@kindex g J / g K (Evil)
@findex majutsu-annotate-next-chunk-same-commit / majutsu-annotate-previous-chunk-same-commit
Move to the next or previous chunk from the same commit.
@item @kbd{@key{RET} (Vanilla)} (@code{majutsu-annotate-show-commit})
@kindex RET (Vanilla)
@findex majutsu-annotate-show-commit
Show the chunk's revision diff.
@item @kbd{M-w} (@code{majutsu-annotate-copy-hash})
