@kindex 1..9
@findex majutsu-conflict-keep-side
Keep side N (the "after" side in JJ diff blocks).
@item @kbd{M-1..M-9} (@code{majutsu-conflict-keep-side})
@kindex M-1..M-9
@findex majutsu-conflict-keep-side
Keep side N's "before" variant.
@item @kbd{R} (@code{majutsu-conflict-refine})
@kindex R
@findex majutsu-conflict-refine
Refine conflict regions with word-level highlighting.
@end table

