@node Understanding Bookmarks
@section Understanding Bookmarks

In Jujutsu@comma{} bookmarks are named references similar to Git branches. A local
bookmark normally targets one revision and may explicitly track a remote
bookmark; concurrent moves can also leave a bookmark with conflicted targets.

