List all bookmarks.
@item @kbd{c} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-create})
@kindex c
@findex majutsu-bookmark-create
Create a new bookmark at point.
@item @kbd{a} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-advance})
@kindex a
@findex majutsu-bookmark-advance
Advance bookmarks using jj's configured default selection and target revset.
@item @kbd{A} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-advance-to})
@kindex A
@findex majutsu-bookmark-advance-to
Advance bookmarks using jj's default selection to an explicit target revset.
@item @kbd{p} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-advance-patterns})
@kindex p
@findex majutsu-bookmark-advance-patterns
Advance specific bookmark name(s)/pattern(s) using jj's configured default target revset.
@item @kbd{s} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-set})
@kindex s
@findex majutsu-bookmark-set
Set or move an existing bookmark to the current revision.
@item @kbd{m} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-move})
@kindex m
@findex majutsu-bookmark-move
Move a bookmark.
@item @kbd{M} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-move-allow-backwards})
@kindex M
