@item @kbd{r} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-rename})
@kindex r
@findex majutsu-bookmark-rename
Rename a bookmark.
@item @kbd{d} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-delete})
@kindex d
@findex majutsu-bookmark-delete
Delete a bookmark locally and record the deletion for propagation on a later push; this command does not contact a remote itself.
@item @kbd{f} (@code{majutsu-bookmark-forget})
@kindex f
